WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

2
00:00:15.458 --> 00:00:16.458
Thank you.

3
00:00:23.958 --> 00:00:25.916
Exactly. This is what I was telling you.

4
00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:28.458
Look. this is her father's wife.

5
00:00:28.541 --> 00:00:29.375
Dad...

6
00:00:29.458 --> 00:00:30.708
Dad. let's go home.

7
00:00:30.791 --> 00:00:31.916
So I can explain...

8
00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:35.160
- What's there to explain?
- Please. let me talk to my Dad!

9
00:00:35.208 --> 00:00:37.458
We saw everything. Just look at him.

10
00:00:37.541 --> 00:00:39.583
He's recovering from seeing that video.

11
00:00:39.666 --> 00:00:41.083
Mom. stop. Just give her a chance.

12
00:00:41.166 --> 00:00:42.875
Will everyone please just shut up!

13
00:00:47.333 --> 00:00:49.291
I'm sorry. I just... I'm sorry.

14
00:00:49.375 --> 00:00:51.215
Thando. do you think this is a joke?

15
00:00:51.250 --> 00:00:53.184
Whoa. whoa. whoa!
Okay. let's... Whoa.

16
00:00:53.208 --> 00:00:55.125
Let's not. Ma. Please.

17
00:00:58.458 --> 00:01:00.916
- Let me help you...
- No! I'm fine.

18
00:01:03.791 --> 00:01:05.166
Dad.

19
00:01:05.250 --> 00:01:06.250
Dad.

20
00:01:16.583 --> 00:01:17.791
How could you?

21
00:01:18.333 --> 00:01:21.166
You couldn't stand the fact
that he chose me over your son. huh?

22
00:01:21.250 --> 00:01:24.125
You think I did this?

23
00:01:26.541 --> 00:01:28.333
So much for being siblings.

24
00:01:29.041 --> 00:01:31.666
Linda. you think I'm responsible for this?

25
00:01:32.250 --> 00:01:33.708
- Linda...
- Phila. you knew?

26
00:01:50.083 --> 00:01:53.375
- Oh! I'm so sorry...
- No issue.

27
00:01:56.375 --> 00:01:57.541
It's you.

28
00:01:58.083 --> 00:01:59.750
Miss Face of Bhengu.

29
00:02:00.666 --> 00:02:01.916
I'm Kolobe.

30
00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:04.833
- Hey. hey. hey. shut up! Shut up!
- It burns!

31
00:02:05.791 --> 00:02:07.125
Uncle!

32
00:02:11.375 --> 00:02:13.000
Are you okay?

33
00:02:24.166 --> 00:02:25.083
I didn't tell her.

34
00:02:25.166 --> 00:02:26.250
I don't believe you.

35
00:02:26.750 --> 00:02:30.208
I told you it was none of my business
what I found out. Nothing's changed.

36
00:02:30.291 --> 00:02:32.000
Everything's changed. Phila.

37
00:02:32.541 --> 00:02:33.583
Come on.

38
00:02:34.166 --> 00:02:35.791
Remember what you said?

39
00:02:35.875 --> 00:02:36.875
Hmm?

40
00:02:37.583 --> 00:02:40.291
How would you feel if
I used your secrets against you?

41
00:02:51.250 --> 00:02:52.750
Zee. talk to me.

42
00:02:52.833 --> 00:02:54.083
<i>It was him.</i>

43
00:02:55.083 --> 00:02:56.333
What are you talking about?

44
00:02:56.416 --> 00:02:57.416
<i>Uncle.</i>

45
00:02:58.125 --> 00:02:59.125
Uncle who?

46
00:02:59.208 --> 00:03:00.916
<i>Uncle. the caretaker.</i>

47
00:03:01.000 --> 00:03:02.125
The one from the house.

48
00:03:02.208 --> 00:03:03.500
Don and Grace's chemist.

49
00:03:03.583 --> 00:03:06.291
Don't lie. are you sure?

50
00:03:06.375 --> 00:03:09.666
I'm telling you.
As soon as I saw his face. I just froze.

51
00:03:11.708 --> 00:03:14.208
<i>Zinhle. can you get
another look just to be sure?</i>

52
00:03:15.083 --> 00:03:16.625
<i>Is he still there?</i>

53
00:03:16.708 --> 00:03:17.708
<i>Zinhle?</i>

54
00:03:18.250 --> 00:03:19.291
Zee?

55
00:03:19.875 --> 00:03:20.875
<i>I'll call you back.</i>

56
00:03:23.166 --> 00:03:24.333
Zinhle?

57
00:03:26.875 --> 00:03:27.916
Zinhle?

58
00:03:47.458 --> 00:03:48.458
Zinhle?

59
00:03:49.125 --> 00:03:50.583
- Hey.
- Hey.

60
00:03:50.666 --> 00:03:52.666
I've been looking for you.

61
00:03:52.750 --> 00:03:55.625
I... I was...
I was trying to catch up with someone.

62
00:03:56.125 --> 00:03:57.125
Okay.

63
00:03:57.500 --> 00:03:59.958
But you're freezing.
let's just talk in the car.

64
00:04:00.041 --> 00:04:00.916
Yeah.

65
00:04:01.000 --> 00:04:02.666
Come on. Get your dress.

66
00:04:11.791 --> 00:04:13.083
I'm sorry.

67
00:04:14.500 --> 00:04:17.458
I don't know what came over me in there.

68
00:04:17.541 --> 00:04:18.708
I just...

69
00:04:20.416 --> 00:04:21.958
I couldn't help myself.

70
00:04:22.458 --> 00:04:23.666
You know. out of...

71
00:04:24.250 --> 00:04:27.000
all the ways I imagined Tata finding out.

72
00:04:27.083 --> 00:04:29.416
I just didn't see this one happening.

73
00:04:32.416 --> 00:04:33.458
Yeah. but I mean.

74
00:04:34.208 --> 00:04:36.666
at least he knows now. right?

75
00:04:36.750 --> 00:04:38.625
How're we going to fix this. Thando?

76
00:04:39.125 --> 00:04:40.333
I don't know.

77
00:04:40.416 --> 00:04:43.666
But all I do know
is that I have to pack my bags tonight.

78
00:04:43.750 --> 00:04:45.250
No. No. no. no. No way.

79
00:04:45.333 --> 00:04:46.833
Don is your father. Linda.

80
00:04:46.916 --> 00:04:47.750
Baby...

81
00:04:47.833 --> 00:04:50.208
You two can easily fix things.
but for me. it's over.

82
00:04:50.291 --> 00:04:53.125
Okay. listen. we're getting
ahead of ourselves here. okay.

83
00:04:53.208 --> 00:04:55.000
Just... Just... Just take it easy.

84
00:04:56.000 --> 00:04:57.708
I'll... I'll fix this.

85
00:04:57.791 --> 00:05:00.750
- Baby. I'll fix this. I'll talk to him.
- No. Look...

86
00:05:00.833 --> 00:05:01.916
Okay.

87
00:05:02.000 --> 00:05:04.333
I can't be with you.
and still be married to your father.

88
00:05:04.416 --> 00:05:05.833
That doesn't make sense.

89
00:05:06.416 --> 00:05:08.416
Choices have to be made now.

90
00:05:23.166 --> 00:05:26.083
- Come on! Why didn't you tell me?
- What? Ma?

91
00:05:27.333 --> 00:05:28.166
Uh...

92
00:05:28.250 --> 00:05:29.791
Ma. it had nothing to do with me.

93
00:05:29.875 --> 00:05:31.083
How long did you know?

94
00:05:31.166 --> 00:05:34.375
About a year.
Geez! I walked in on them in Linda's room.

95
00:05:34.958 --> 00:05:37.166
A year! Under my roof?

96
00:05:37.666 --> 00:05:39.416
Well. more like a year and a half.

97
00:05:40.041 --> 00:05:42.583
After I saw them.
they became extra careful.

98
00:05:43.625 --> 00:05:44.916
How did this even happen?

99
00:05:45.416 --> 00:05:47.833
Sometime after Thando lost the baby.

100
00:05:48.500 --> 00:05:51.375
Linda was there for her.
Ma. they fell in love.

101
00:05:51.458 --> 00:05:52.708
That's disgusting.

102
00:05:53.375 --> 00:05:55.541
Have you
seen the headline? Look.

103
00:05:55.625 --> 00:05:58.750
"Bhengu Daughter
Steals Father's Wife." Bloody circus.

104
00:05:58.833 --> 00:05:59.833
Ma...

105
00:06:00.375 --> 00:06:01.416
And Dad?

106
00:06:01.500 --> 00:06:02.750
What does he say?

107
00:06:03.625 --> 00:06:04.750
Hasn't said a word.

108
00:06:06.166 --> 00:06:07.750
I wonder how many people knew.

109
00:06:07.833 --> 00:06:11.666
An affair like this
is perfect ammunition for our enemies.

110
00:06:11.750 --> 00:06:14.916
At least your father
can't keep Linda as CEO now.

111
00:06:15.000 --> 00:06:16.333
Ma. too soon.

112
00:06:16.416 --> 00:06:17.750
Oh. like hell it is.

113
00:06:17.833 --> 00:06:19.375
We all have to play our part.

114
00:06:19.458 --> 00:06:22.750
I'll deal with this PR nightmare.
find out who's behind it.

115
00:06:23.250 --> 00:06:26.958
But you. on the other hand.
you've been given another chance.

116
00:06:27.041 --> 00:06:29.416
Get off your high horse
and support your father.

117
00:06:52.250 --> 00:06:53.416
I'm sorry I'm late.

118
00:06:53.500 --> 00:06:55.750
- Just hurry up with the papers.
- Okay.

119
00:06:56.375 --> 00:06:58.041
Should be simple enough.

120
00:06:59.500 --> 00:07:01.041
No. She won't contest it.

121
00:07:04.208 --> 00:07:05.208
You...

122
00:07:06.166 --> 00:07:07.666
You deserve nothing.

123
00:07:08.166 --> 00:07:09.875
Once you sign this paperwork.

124
00:07:10.583 --> 00:07:13.083
you'll be a nobody with nothing.

125
00:07:15.416 --> 00:07:16.625
That's fine with me.

126
00:07:16.708 --> 00:07:18.916
All I ever wanted was my freedom. anyway.

127
00:07:20.375 --> 00:07:22.875
Aren't you going to ask
why I fell in love with Linda?

128
00:07:23.708 --> 00:07:30.000
See. unlike you.
she's kind. loving. and sensitive.

129
00:07:32.250 --> 00:07:34.875
So you'd notice that.
if you weren't so controlling.

130
00:07:37.625 --> 00:07:38.791
And another thing.

131
00:07:39.666 --> 00:07:42.250
she satisfies me in <i>every</i> way.

132
00:07:43.583 --> 00:07:47.166
Something the great Don
couldn't even get right.

133
00:07:47.666 --> 00:07:50.208
Get the hell out of my house.

134
00:07:54.875 --> 00:07:56.000
Hey. girl!

135
00:07:56.916 --> 00:07:58.041
The ring.

136
00:08:03.291 --> 00:08:05.083
With pleasure.

137
00:08:15.541 --> 00:08:16.625
Zinhle?

138
00:08:18.458 --> 00:08:19.750
Where are you going?

139
00:08:19.833 --> 00:08:21.833
You also running away
from the drama in this house?

140
00:08:21.916 --> 00:08:22.791
Uh. no.

141
00:08:22.875 --> 00:08:24.791
I already had plans with my friends.

142
00:08:24.875 --> 00:08:26.333
Oh. Okay.

143
00:08:26.416 --> 00:08:27.666
You and Linda...

144
00:08:27.750 --> 00:08:29.190
Never would've guessed.

145
00:08:30.166 --> 00:08:33.333
Yeah. I wanted to tell you. but...

146
00:08:33.416 --> 00:08:35.958
You know. how does
someone drop a bomb like that?

147
00:08:36.041 --> 00:08:37.125
Do you love her?

148
00:08:38.791 --> 00:08:40.000
Very much.

149
00:08:41.333 --> 00:08:43.253
I just wish
it came out differently.

150
00:08:43.291 --> 00:08:45.208
but you know Grace
had to be a bitch about it.

151
00:08:45.791 --> 00:08:48.500
- You think she's behind the video?
- Yeah. of course.

152
00:08:48.583 --> 00:08:50.083
Who else could it be?

153
00:08:50.166 --> 00:08:52.750
She hates that Don chose Linda to be CEO...

154
00:08:52.833 --> 00:08:56.666
And he wanted to have
more kids with me. so the bitch snapped.

155
00:08:56.750 --> 00:08:58.083
Wow.

156
00:08:58.166 --> 00:09:00.208
Yeah. I'm finally free!

157
00:09:00.291 --> 00:09:02.166
What?

158
00:09:02.208 --> 00:09:03.666
No. I don't care.

159
00:09:03.750 --> 00:09:06.208
You know. Don didn't want
to let me go for like a year.

160
00:09:06.291 --> 00:09:09.291
I tried to speak to him when
I heard he was getting married again.

161
00:09:09.375 --> 00:09:10.416
Again?

162
00:09:10.500 --> 00:09:13.500
Yeah. Not immediately.
but he does want to have more kids.

163
00:09:13.583 --> 00:09:17.208
But I am finally off the hook.

164
00:09:17.291 --> 00:09:18.958
So you're really leaving?

165
00:09:19.458 --> 00:09:20.818
He called the lawyer.

166
00:09:22.416 --> 00:09:24.616
I don't think I'll be here
when you come back.

167
00:09:25.666 --> 00:09:26.946
I'm gonna miss you.

168
00:09:27.000 --> 00:09:30.333
Ah. stop being dramatic about it.
It's not like I'm going to Iceland.

169
00:09:30.416 --> 00:09:32.000
I'll still see you around.

170
00:09:32.083 --> 00:09:34.291
But thank you
for being a good buddy.

171
00:09:35.666 --> 00:09:38.458
Come here.
Bring it in. bring it in. bring it in.

172
00:09:46.500 --> 00:09:49.333
We have to find out
what he does for Don and Grace.

173
00:09:49.416 --> 00:09:51.333
He introduced himself as Kolobe.

174
00:09:51.416 --> 00:09:54.000
I looked him up online
but couldn't find anything.

175
00:09:54.083 --> 00:09:57.291
You need his full name.

176
00:09:58.541 --> 00:09:59.666
Will you be okay?

177
00:10:00.708 --> 00:10:01.708
Yeah.

178
00:10:01.791 --> 00:10:04.208
- I'll be fine.
- I know you really liked him.

179
00:10:04.791 --> 00:10:06.916
That's when I thought he was a good man.

180
00:10:09.000 --> 00:10:11.458
That's why you can't trust anyone.

181
00:10:11.541 --> 00:10:13.083
Yeah.

182
00:10:13.125 --> 00:10:16.125
That's why you should stop
whatever you and Ndu are doing.

183
00:10:17.208 --> 00:10:20.000
I told you there's nothing going on.

184
00:10:21.166 --> 00:10:22.166
I have to go.

185
00:10:22.208 --> 00:10:24.125
I'll let you know when I find his name.

186
00:10:24.208 --> 00:10:25.208
Bye.

187
00:10:48.583 --> 00:10:49.583
Tata.

188
00:10:50.166 --> 00:10:52.791
Here is a notice
of resignation. Sign it...

189
00:10:53.583 --> 00:10:55.125
And get out of my house.

190
00:10:55.791 --> 00:10:57.250
Just like that?

191
00:11:02.958 --> 00:11:05.833
You can't make a decision like that
without talking to me first.

192
00:11:05.916 --> 00:11:07.333
Are you the man now?

193
00:11:08.583 --> 00:11:09.583
Huh?

194
00:11:10.666 --> 00:11:11.916
First. you sleep with my wife

195
00:11:12.000 --> 00:11:14.750
and now you're telling me
what I can and what I can't do!

196
00:11:17.375 --> 00:11:21.250
My role in this company
has nothing to do with Thando and I.

197
00:11:22.750 --> 00:11:24.833
Grace did all of this. Dad.

198
00:11:24.916 --> 00:11:26.500
Why can't you not...

199
00:11:28.833 --> 00:11:30.000
I love you.

200
00:11:31.166 --> 00:11:33.458
I... I respect you so much. and...

201
00:11:36.916 --> 00:11:38.125
My...

202
00:11:38.208 --> 00:11:40.041
My relationship with Thando...

203
00:11:40.125 --> 00:11:42.208
- I tried...
- Thando is my wife!

204
00:11:43.208 --> 00:11:44.416
She was my wife!

205
00:11:45.500 --> 00:11:47.500
You could've had
any other girl in Jo'burg!

206
00:11:47.583 --> 00:11:48.916
We fell in love. Dad.

207
00:11:53.791 --> 00:11:55.208
You didn't love her. so...

208
00:12:02.000 --> 00:12:04.000
I never liked that picture.

209
00:12:14.166 --> 00:12:18.000
Letting you
marry my husband was a mistake.

210
00:12:18.500 --> 00:12:19.875
"Letting you?"

211
00:12:22.750 --> 00:12:25.708
It's not like you had a choice. Gracey.

212
00:12:26.791 --> 00:12:28.750
There's that big mouth again.

213
00:12:28.833 --> 00:12:30.873
You've been disrespectful from day one.

214
00:12:30.916 --> 00:12:32.916
No. you've been
mistreating me from day one.

215
00:12:33.000 --> 00:12:34.916
Because you needed to know your place.

216
00:12:36.208 --> 00:12:39.250
When are you going to stop being so weak

217
00:12:39.333 --> 00:12:40.500
where Don's concerned?

218
00:12:41.708 --> 00:12:43.541
You're better than this.

219
00:12:48.208 --> 00:12:51.291
You'll never get the kind of love
you need from Don.

220
00:12:51.375 --> 00:12:53.458
You'll have to imagine it.

221
00:12:57.166 --> 00:12:59.833
But I'll call to coordinate the movers.

222
00:12:59.916 --> 00:13:01.166
Thank you. Sisi.

223
00:13:05.666 --> 00:13:06.666
Sis'...

224
00:13:08.375 --> 00:13:10.055
You can't leave like this.

225
00:13:10.083 --> 00:13:11.083
What you want me to do?

226
00:13:11.166 --> 00:13:13.125
Can't we just
sit down and talk about this?

227
00:13:16.791 --> 00:13:18.583
Ndu. it's done. okay?

228
00:13:19.875 --> 00:13:21.708
Dad made himself very clear.

229
00:13:21.791 --> 00:13:24.041
Okay. Thando. Thando. let's fix this.

230
00:13:24.125 --> 00:13:27.916
You can't fix this family. Ndu.
But I'll miss you. though.

231
00:13:28.000 --> 00:13:29.666
- Listen. sis'...
- Whoa.

232
00:13:29.750 --> 00:13:31.333
- Bro.
- Dude. that's it?

233
00:13:31.416 --> 00:13:33.375
We can't give up on each other like this.

234
00:13:33.458 --> 00:13:35.208
We've all made mistakes here.

235
00:13:36.500 --> 00:13:39.833
There's someone evil behind this.
and we can't let them win. man

236
00:13:39.916 --> 00:13:41.708
I don't make the decisions around here.

237
00:13:42.541 --> 00:13:43.541
Come on. Mom?

238
00:13:43.583 --> 00:13:45.583
Did you really have to take the cars too?

239
00:14:30.250 --> 00:14:32.375
Okay. babe.
And then? Why did we stop?

240
00:14:35.416 --> 00:14:37.250
What if Phila didn't tell Grace?

241
00:14:37.333 --> 00:14:40.500
Yes. Phila didn't tell Grace.
She found out some other way.

242
00:14:41.000 --> 00:14:42.041
No. no. no. wait. Wait.

243
00:14:42.125 --> 00:14:45.041
The more I think about this.
the more I have so many questions.

244
00:14:45.125 --> 00:14:46.125
Okay. look.

245
00:14:47.208 --> 00:14:49.416
Grace wouldn't have
revealed this all publicly.

246
00:14:49.500 --> 00:14:50.666
You know how she's like.

247
00:14:51.166 --> 00:14:52.583
Yeah. maybe she was desperate.

248
00:14:52.666 --> 00:14:55.291
Remember. Phila lost out to you.

249
00:14:56.541 --> 00:15:00.083
And now that I think about it.
if it wasn't Grace. then who was it?

250
00:15:04.833 --> 00:15:07.250
I don't know.
but I'm sure as hell gonna find out.

251
00:15:08.875 --> 00:15:11.541
Angela's interviewing us tomorrow.

252
00:15:12.125 --> 00:15:14.708
It will help us present a united front.

253
00:15:15.458 --> 00:15:16.500
Why her?

254
00:15:17.000 --> 00:15:18.458
She's critical of us.

255
00:15:18.958 --> 00:15:21.041
But in this situation. that's a bonus.

256
00:15:21.666 --> 00:15:23.750
We'll appear to be transparent.

257
00:15:28.250 --> 00:15:30.916
Has this thing
with Linda affected business?

258
00:15:31.916 --> 00:15:33.750
Any reaction from the partners?

259
00:15:35.708 --> 00:15:37.541
Are you responsible for the video?

260
00:15:38.875 --> 00:15:41.375
Oh Don. that's not my style.

261
00:15:42.583 --> 00:15:44.000
If I knew...

