Don't.

525
00:37:02.041 --> 00:37:03.333
Stop! Kolobe. stop. stop.

526
00:37:03.375 --> 00:37:04.541
What's wrong?

527
00:37:06.833 --> 00:37:08.000
I can't do this.

528
00:37:08.708 --> 00:37:11.833
- You can. You're the one who called me.
- It was a mistake.

529
00:37:12.666 --> 00:37:13.541
Grace.

530
00:37:13.625 --> 00:37:16.351
What do you get being faithful
to a man who doesn't touch you anymore?

531
00:37:16.375 --> 00:37:17.875
Ah. Be careful of what you're saying.

532
00:37:17.958 --> 00:37:19.208
He doesn't want you.

533
00:37:19.291 --> 00:37:20.811
And I won't wait forever.

534
00:37:22.708 --> 00:37:23.583
Uh...

535
00:37:23.666 --> 00:37:25.500
He doesn't respect you. Grace.

536
00:37:25.583 --> 00:37:27.743
Even after
everything you've done for him.

537
00:37:28.166 --> 00:37:30.541
Why are you
wasting your life with someone...

538
00:37:30.625 --> 00:37:33.791
Wait. Don't you dare lecture me.

539
00:37:34.375 --> 00:37:36.083
About wasting my time.

540
00:37:36.166 --> 00:37:38.666
What have you
been doing all this time?

541
00:37:38.750 --> 00:37:40.750
Obsessing
over another man's wife?

542
00:37:40.833 --> 00:37:42.375
What kind of man does that?

543
00:37:42.458 --> 00:37:44.833
Then you spend years
serving Don like some garden boy?

544
00:37:44.916 --> 00:37:45.833
Don't do that.

545
00:37:45.916 --> 00:37:47.041
Listen. Kolobe.

546
00:37:48.791 --> 00:37:50.875
I have money.

547
00:37:50.958 --> 00:37:53.333
I have children. I have everything.

548
00:37:54.000 --> 00:37:56.125
And a real man for a husband.

549
00:37:56.208 --> 00:37:57.416
What about you?

550
00:37:57.500 --> 00:37:59.125
What do you have?

551
00:37:59.208 --> 00:38:00.708
- What do you have?
- Don't do this.

552
00:38:00.791 --> 00:38:02.208
You have nothing.

553
00:40:30.083 --> 00:40:31.458
<i>Hello.</i>

554
00:40:31.541 --> 00:40:33.250
- Don.
<i>- Kolobe.</i>

555
00:40:33.333 --> 00:40:34.333
Sure.

556
00:40:35.583 --> 00:40:37.833
I think you were
right when you said that...

557
00:40:38.333 --> 00:40:40.708
...we should
move the factory to China.

558
00:40:40.791 --> 00:40:42.000
I think we should do it...

559
00:40:42.750 --> 00:40:43.750
for good.

560
00:40:45.500 --> 00:40:47.458
<i>Let's talk about it tomorrow.</i>

561
00:41:17.250 --> 00:41:20.416
<i>And a real man
for a husband. What about you?</i>

562
00:41:20.958 --> 00:41:22.250
<i>What do you have?</i>

563
00:41:22.750 --> 00:41:24.208
<i>What do you have?</i>

564
00:41:28.833 --> 00:41:30.000
<i>What do you have?</i>

565
00:41:34.750 --> 00:41:37.166
How many beaches have you been to?

566
00:41:38.041 --> 00:41:39.291
In South Africa?

567
00:41:45.791 --> 00:41:47.333
I don't know. I've been to many.

568
00:41:49.833 --> 00:41:51.916
And you? What did you do growing up?

569
00:41:52.583 --> 00:41:54.500
Well. not beaches.

570
00:41:55.000 --> 00:41:56.333
My sister...

571
00:41:57.125 --> 00:41:59.375
she'd always pretend to be a TV presenter.

572
00:41:59.458 --> 00:42:01.083
and my brother would complain.

573
00:42:01.166 --> 00:42:04.291
And every time he complained.
she'd do it even more.

574
00:42:05.708 --> 00:42:06.791
It was fun.

575
00:42:08.916 --> 00:42:11.000
I thought you said you only had a sister.

576
00:42:13.000 --> 00:42:14.083
Um...

577
00:42:15.875 --> 00:42:17.750
He was... He was my cousin.

578
00:42:18.375 --> 00:42:20.708
but he felt like a sibling. you know?

579
00:42:23.833 --> 00:42:25.208
The one who passed away?

580
00:42:27.583 --> 00:42:29.916
I'm actually a bit thirsty.

581
00:42:30.000 --> 00:42:31.541
Can you get me some water?

582
00:42:32.583 --> 00:42:33.625
Yeah. sure.

583
00:42:53.041 --> 00:42:54.333
<i>Zinhle. look.</i>

584
00:42:59.416 --> 00:43:00.708
<i>We've got them.</i>

585
00:43:02.041 --> 00:43:03.166
<i>Look.</i>

586
00:43:04.125 --> 00:43:05.208
<i>Look.</i>

587
00:43:13.750 --> 00:43:14.875
- Bro.
<i>- Sure.</i>

588
00:43:15.958 --> 00:43:17.541
<i>Did you see the video?</i>

589
00:43:17.625 --> 00:43:20.791
- Yes. are you sure?
<i>- Yes. I'm sure.</i>

590
00:43:20.875 --> 00:43:27.333
<i>I broke into Kolobe's house
and heard him talk to Don about it.</i>

591
00:43:28.083 --> 00:43:30.458
<i>They're moving operations to China.</i>

592
00:43:30.541 --> 00:43:32.666
<i>We need to make sure that we expose them.</i>

593
00:43:34.125 --> 00:43:35.375
Shit. Uh...

594
00:43:36.916 --> 00:43:39.041
Okay. I'll call you back.

595
00:43:59.541 --> 00:44:01.333
So you've got options.

596
00:44:01.416 --> 00:44:03.333
You've got your strawberry.
you've got kiwi.

597
00:44:03.416 --> 00:44:05.625
you got your peach.
and you got your dairy too.

598
00:44:06.166 --> 00:44:07.625
And your favorite...

599
00:44:08.500 --> 00:44:09.625
Desmarais.

600
00:44:16.583 --> 00:44:17.708
Ndumi...

601
00:44:17.791 --> 00:44:19.250
Can I tell you a secret?

602
00:44:26.875 --> 00:44:28.435
Zinhle. I'm falling for you.

603
00:44:30.916 --> 00:44:34.750
I've had my eyes on you
from the very first time I saw you...

604
00:44:34.833 --> 00:44:36.458
I can't be with you. Ndu.

605
00:44:37.666 --> 00:44:38.666
It's over.

606
00:44:42.791 --> 00:44:43.791
Excuse me?

607
00:44:44.500 --> 00:44:45.791
I'm done.

608
00:44:46.750 --> 00:44:48.017
You must be joking...

609
00:44:48.041 --> 00:44:50.851
- We had an amazing day...
- You and I have different lives.

610
00:44:50.875 --> 00:44:53.000
And I need to focus on my priorities.

611
00:44:53.083 --> 00:44:55.666
Okay. whoa. whoa! Zinhle. slow down.

612
00:44:55.750 --> 00:44:57.416
Just let it go!

613
00:44:58.000 --> 00:45:00.416
We come from different worlds.
and that's that.

614
00:45:01.458 --> 00:45:04.375
So. tomorrow let's focus on work.

615
00:45:04.875 --> 00:45:06.083
And get back home.

616
00:45:06.166 --> 00:45:07.083
Zinhle...

617
00:45:07.166 --> 00:45:09.125
I don't want to talk about this again.

618
00:45:10.708 --> 00:45:12.250
I'll sleep in the other room.

619
00:45:13.041 --> 00:45:14.041
Don't come in.

620
00:45:31.458 --> 00:45:32.750
<i>We believe in honesty.</i>

621
00:45:33.750 --> 00:45:36.458
<i>loyalty and trust above everything else.</i>

622
00:45:37.625 --> 00:45:42.208
<i>We want our colleagues and customers
to know how much we value family.</i>

623
00:45:43.833 --> 00:45:46.958
<i>We will not support or condone anything</i>

624
00:45:47.041 --> 00:45:49.708
<i>that seeks to undermine the family unit.</i>

625
00:45:51.291 --> 00:45:52.541
<i>There you have it.</i>

626
00:45:52.625 --> 00:45:56.250
<i>D & G Bhengu projecting a united front</i>

627
00:45:56.333 --> 00:45:58.625
<i>after their very sudden revelation.</i>

628
00:45:58.708 --> 00:46:02.083
<i>I'm Angela Makwetu. a good one to you all.</i>

629
00:46:13.291 --> 00:46:14.291
Baby?

630
00:46:15.166 --> 00:46:16.500
- Babe?
- Mmm.

631
00:46:19.250 --> 00:46:21.625
You know what. I'm...
I'm more than convinced now

632
00:46:21.708 --> 00:46:23.958
that Grace and Phila
had nothing to do with this.

633
00:46:24.541 --> 00:46:27.750
Obviously. Ndu and Tata
are ruled out. but I just...

634
00:46:28.541 --> 00:46:30.083
Yeah. and...

635
00:46:35.291 --> 00:46:38.500
You and. um...
Zinhle are quite close. right?

636
00:46:40.458 --> 00:46:41.500
Right?

637
00:46:43.708 --> 00:46:45.041
Yeah.

638
00:46:45.125 --> 00:46:47.041
Okay. so maybe do you think...

639
00:46:47.666 --> 00:46:51.666
if you remember at any point.
did you let it slip about us?

640
00:46:52.333 --> 00:46:53.333
Uh...

641
00:46:53.708 --> 00:46:56.375
Babe. are you seriously
trying to accuse Zinhle?

642
00:46:56.458 --> 00:46:58.333
I'm not trying to accuse her of anything.

643
00:46:58.416 --> 00:47:00.666
Just saying.
she's the only outsider in the house.

644
00:47:00.750 --> 00:47:03.541
Why would she film us?
Why would she want to expose us?

645
00:47:03.625 --> 00:47:04.541
I don't know.

646
00:47:04.625 --> 00:47:07.666
I can't believe you woke me up
for this nonsense. babe. Uh-uh.

647
00:47:07.750 --> 00:47:10.208
Thando. I just don't think
we should rule her out.

648
00:47:10.750 --> 00:47:11.875
Look. look...

649
00:47:12.666 --> 00:47:14.583
I know what happened was awful.

650
00:47:15.541 --> 00:47:19.416
But accusing Zinhle is just crazy now.

651
00:47:21.708 --> 00:47:23.125
I want to go to sleep.

